### 4.3 Key AI Tasks

The AI agent performs several tasks to analyze housing listings and extract relevant information.

#### Text Analysis

The system reads listing descriptions, captions, and comments from housing platforms and social media posts.
Listings may contain multiple languages, such as Spanish or English.

#### Feature Detection

The AI agent detects important signals within listing text.

Examples include:

- Empadronamiento compatibility
- Accommodation type
- Price information
- Location references
- Minimum stay duration

*Example signal detected:*

"You can register your residency at this property"

This is interpreted as:
Empadronamiento Status: Allowed

#### Opportunity Filtering

After signals are detected, the system filters listings based on:

- Empadronamiento compatibility
- User housing preferences
- Location (Barcelona)

Listings where empadronamiento is not allowed are excluded.

