### 4.5 Technical Approach

The system uses a combination of data collection and AI-based text analysis.

Key components include:

- Listing aggregation from multiple sources
- Text extraction from listings
- AI-based signal detection
- Multilingual phrase recognition
- Structured output generation

The AI agent focuses on detecting administrative compatibility signals such as empadronamiento, which are currently hidden in listing descriptions.
By transforming unstructured listing text into structured signals, the system enables users to identify housing opportunities more efficiently.
